{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3184800/extras/battle2.gif?t=1734725872\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">This is the demo version of Wildkeepers Rising, a roguelite RPG bullet heaven where you tame and train a diverse team of Guardian beasts to destroy the invading monster hordes. In the game, you\u2019ll face hand-drawn fantasy monsters inspired by the worlds of Akira Toriyama and Jim Henson.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">In this demo you'll have access to the first 2-3 hours of gameplay, including the first map, 12 different Guardians and 2 playable characters. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3184800/extras/allbuffs-optimize.gif?t=1734725872\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Bullet Heaven </strong> | Shred thousands of monsters in bullet heaven runs</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Creature Collector</strong> | Discover, tame, and train magical beasts</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Runs &amp; Builds</strong> | Create team synergies with different Guardians</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Roguelike Runs</strong> | Take runs with different Wildkeepers wielding different weapons</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Progression</strong> | Unlock new Guardians and items and make them stronger between runs</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>RPG Elements</strong> | Discover a rich world of fantasy heroes and magical monsters.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3184800/extras/Grampth_Idle-optimize2.gif?t=1734725872\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Meet the Developers</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Lioncode Games is an indie development duo making Wildkeep